data.text: Actively monitoring the #CrucesFire near Lompoc – thank you to our first responders who are working to contain the blaze. Evacuations have been ordered on the 7200 block of Highway 1 & Highway 1 is closed from Highway 101 to Highway 246. https://t.co/HoKxV4ufRR
